Open the project currently using domain salon-ruwan.vercel.app.
Set Root Directory to repository root . (not backend / web).
Keep root config from vercel.json.
In this same project, set env vars (MONGODB_URI, JWT_SECRET, CLIENT_URL, NODE_ENV, VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api).
In Domains, attach salon-ruwan.vercel.app to this root project and remove it from backend-only project if attached there.
Redeploy latest commit.{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "backend/api/index.ts",
      "use": "@vercel/node"
    },
    {
      "src": "web/package.json",
      "use": "@vercel/static-build",
      "config": {
        "buildCommand": "npm --prefix web run build",
        "installCommand": "npm install",
        "distDir": "dist"
      }
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/api",
      "dest": "/backend/api/index"
    },
    {
      "src": "/api/(.*)",
      "dest": "/backend/api/index"
    },
    {
      "handle": "filesystem"
    },
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "/index.html"
    }
  ]
}